---

<BaseLayout title="Curved Conveyors: Roller Curves, Belt Curves &#x26; Modular Belt Turns" description="Complete guide to curved conveyors: tapered roller curves, belt curves, modular belt turns, gravity curves, product orientation, and minimum radius for packaging and distribution." canonical="https://packagingconveyor.com/conveyor-types/curved-conveyors/" schema={[breadcrumbSchema, faqSchema, articleSchema]}>

  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
